description: Demolition of raised podium deck, existing day nursery, management office and associated structures. Redevelopment of the site involving the creation of a replacement day nursery and external play area (Use Class D1) along with provision of 89 residential units (Use Class C3) in buildings ranging from 1 to 16 storeys in height; public realm improvements; parking and servicing space; creation of new vehicular and pedestrian accesses; and associated works.
